debian-installer-utils (1.116) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * vt102-di: Tinker vt102 entry, to avoid using ^J, since various levels of
    tty may be adding a ^M and thus scrambling the output, use generic escape
    sequence instead.

